long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Do you spend 10 minutes before a meeting, making sure that you don’t miss that meeting? Do you struggle to stay in the flow right before those meetings? Well I do. I created this chrome that will call the you when your meeting starts by opening your google meet meetings with a ringtone. Now, you can concentrate on coding, product managing, data sciencing, or whatever, up until right before your meeting.
